e the amount of data processed in joins.\n- **Join Condition Optimization**: Ensure that join conditions are efficiently utilized.\n- **Subquery Optimization**: Consider transforming the subquery to reduce correlation or materialize it if possible.\n\n### Selected Rewrite Rules:\n1. **FILTER_INTO_JOIN**: Push filter expressions into the join condition to reduce the data processed by the join.\n2. **JOIN_CONDITION_PUSH**: Push predicates in a join into the inputs to the join to optimize join processing.\n3. **FILTER_AGGREGATE_TRANSPOSE**: Push filters past aggregates if applicable, to reduce the data processed by the aggregate functions.\n\n### Transformation Steps:\n1. **Apply FILTER_INTO_JOIN**: Push the filter conditions related to `i_item_sk` and `d_date_sk` into the join conditions. This reduces the data processed by the join.\n2. **Apply JOIN_CONDITION_PUSH**: Ensure that join conditions are efficiently utilized by pushing predicates into the join inputs.\n3. **Apply FILTER_AGGREGATE_TRANSPOSE**: If applicable, push filters past aggregates to reduce the data processed by the aggregate functions.\n\n### Optimized Query:\n```sql\nSELECT \n   SUM(ws_ext_discount_amt) AS "Excess Discount Amount"\nFROM\n   web_sales\nJOIN\n   item ON i_item_sk = ws_item_sk\nJOIN\n   date_dim ON d_date_sk = ws_sold_date_sk\nWHERE\n   (i_manufact_id BETWEEN 761 AND 960 OR i_category IN (\'Books\', \'Children\', \'Home\'))\n   AND d_date BETWEEN \'1998-02-08\' AND CAST(\'1998-02-08\' AS DATE) + INTERVAL \'90\' DAY\n   AND ws_wholesale_cost BETWEEN 61 AND 81\n   AND ws_ext_discount_amt > (\n      SELECT\n         1.3 * AVG(ws_ext_discount_amt)\n      FROM\n         web_sales\n      JOIN\n         date_dim ON d_date_sk = ws_sold_date_sk\n      WHERE\n         ws_item_sk = i_item_sk\n         AND d_date BETWEEN \'1998-02-08\' AND CAST(\'1998-02-08\' AS DATE) + INTERVAL \'90\' DAY\n         AND ws_wholesale_cost BETWEEN 61 AND 81\n         AND ws_sales_price / ws_list_price BETWEEN 0.43 AND 0.58\n   )\nORDER BY SUM(ws_ext_discount_amt)\nLIMIT 100;\n```\n\n### Selected Rules:\n```python\n[\n    "FILTER_INTO_JOIN",\n    "JOIN_CONDITION_PUSH",\n    "FILTER_AGGREGATE_TRANSPOSE"\n]\n```', 'time': 9.346202373504639}
